Step 3: xpath লিখো (field add / modify)

Real examples (most important part)

Example 1: নতুন field add করতে চাই

<xpath expr="//group" position="inside">
    <field name="my_custom_field"/>
</xpath>

Example 2: Specific field-এর পরে add করতে চাই
<xpath expr="//field[@name='phone']" position="after">
    <field name="other_phone"/>
</xpath>
Example 3: Existing field hide করতে চাই
<xpath expr="//field[@name='email_from']" position="attributes">
    <attribute name="invisible">1</attribute>
</xpath>
Example 4: Label change করতে চাই
<xpath expr="//field[@name='phone']" position="attributes">
    <attribute name="string">Mobile Number</attribute>
</xpath>
Example 5: Notebook-এ নতুন page add
<xpath expr="//notebook" position="inside">
    <page string="Extra Info">
        <group>
            <field name="x_note"/>
        </group>
    </page>
</xpath>


